Package: toy
Title: A Toy R Package for Reporting Tables in Safety Statistics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Automates the creation of reporting tables for safety statistics 
  using standardized input datasets like ADaMs. Includes tables for demographics, 
  disposition, adverse reactions, AE summaries, specific AEs, and more.
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
